3. Mandatory conditions of use
------------------------------
- UNOFFICIAL. This is an unofficial fan app. It is not published or endorsed by
  Autarch LLC and does not present itself as an official Autarch product. The
  app's own name and its developer's identity are kept more prominent than
  "ACKS II".
- FREE. The app is free to access and use: no purchase price, subscription,
  premium tier, paywall, paid early access, advertising, affiliate links, paid
  API, or required crowdfunding contribution. Voluntary donations, if accepted,
  earn the donor no extra features, content, releases, or support.
- USERS STILL NEED THE BOOKS. Users must legitimately own the ACKS II
  publications this app requires. The app is not marketed as a replacement for
  buying them and does not knowingly help users avoid buying them.
- CONTENT STAYS INSIDE THE APP. ACKS II content is not published separately: no
  data dumps, protected-content repositories, bulk exports, public APIs exposing
  substantial content, downloadable embeddings, or tools designed to reconstruct
  the books. Reasonable safeguards against scraping and extraction apply.
- AI LIMITS. AI may assist development and power in-app features using ACKS II
  material only inside this approved app. ACKS II material is not used to train or
  fine-tune a model, is not retained by a provider without written approval, is
  not released as a general-purpose ACKS model or exposed retrieval database, and
  is not used to reconstruct the books.


